        <p>On the northbound side I would really like to see the frontage road start at San Jacinto rather than
        Wheeler, but that would require the removal of the entire Mexican Consulate building. (It is unclear to me if that building needs to be acquired with the current plan, but it appears not.) So I'm still hoping for as much frontage road as possible in the next plan.
            </p>
    </div>

